{"version": 2, "width": 80, "height": 24, "timestamp": 1774315862, "env": {"SHELL": "/bin/bash", "TERM": "xterm-256color"}}
[0.00383, "o", "\u001b[H\u001b[2J\u001b[3J"]
[0.004462, "o", "\r\n  ╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\r\n  ║                                                   ║\r\n  ║   🛡️  MCP Shield Demo                             ║\r\n  ║   One-command security for MCP servers            ║\r\n  ║   Powered by agentgateway                         ║\r\n  ║                                                   ║\r\n  ╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\r\n\r\n"]
[3.006153, "o", "  📋 Step 1: Here's a typical insecure MCP setup\r\n\r\n"]
[4.010452, "o", "{\r\n  \"mcpServers\": {\r\n    \"filesystem\": {\r\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\r\n      \"args\": [\"-y\", \"@modelcontextprotocol/server-filesystem\", \"/tmp\"]\r\n    },\r\n    \"memory\": {\r\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\r\n      \"args\": [\"-y\", \"@modelcontextprotocol/server-memory\"]\r\n    },\r\n    \"github\": {\r\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\r\n      \"args\": [\"-y\", \"@modelcontextprotocol/server-github\"],\r\n      \"env\": {\r\n        \"GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN\": \"ghp_xxxxx\"\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n"]
[7.012582, "o", "\r\n  ⚠️  Problem: No auth, no rate limits, no logging!\r\n\r\n"]
[9.013827, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m$ node dist/index.js scan -f demo/sample-config.json\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[10.093127, "o", "\r\n🔍 Scanning for MCP server configurations...\r\n\r\n"]
[10.093404, "o", "  📁 Source:  claude-desktop\r\n  📄 File:    demo/sample-config.json\r\n  🔧 Servers: 3 found\r\n\r\n  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\r\n  │ MCP Servers                                            │\r\n  ├────────────────────┬──────────┬────────────────────────┤\r\n  │ Name               │ Type     │ Command/URL            │\r\n  ├────────────────────┼──────────┼────────────────────────┤\r\n  │ filesystem         │ stdio    │ npx                    │\r\n  │ memory             │ stdio    │ npx                    │\r\n"]
[10.09347, "o", "  │ github             │ stdio    │ npx                    │\r\n  └────────────────────┴──────────┴────────────────────────┘\r\n\r\n  ⚠️  Security Assessment:\r\n    • Authentication:  NONE — any client can connect\r\n"]
[10.093489, "o", "    • Rate Limiting:   NONE — no protection against abuse\r\n    • Audit Logging:   NONE — no visibility into tool usage\r\n    • Input Validation: NONE — tool arguments pass unchecked\r\n\r\n"]
[10.093653, "o", "  💡 Run 'mcp-shield secure' to generate a secured configuration.\r\n\r\n"]
[12.104859, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m$ node dist/index.js secure -f demo/sample-config.json --rate-limit 60\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[13.143269, "o", "\r\n🛡️  MCP Shield — Generating secured configuration...\r\n\r\n"]
[13.143529, "o", "  📁 Found 3 MCP server(s) from claude-desktop\r\n\r\n"]
[13.143721, "o", "  🔐 Generating JWT keypair for authentication...\r\n"]
[13.148114, "o", "     Public key:  mcp-shield-output/keys/pub-key\r\n     Private key: mcp-shield-output/keys/priv-key.pem\r\n\r\n"]
[13.154497, "o", "  ✅ Secured configuration generated!\r\n\r\n  📂 Output files:\r\n     mcp-shield-output/gateway-config.yaml  — agentgateway configuration\r\n     mcp-shield-output/claude_desktop_config.json  — client config (points to gateway)\r\n     mcp-shield-output/keys/  — JWT keypair\r\n\r\n  🚀 To start the secured gateway:\r\n\r\n     agentgateway -f mcp-shield-output/gateway-config.yaml\r\n\r\n  Then update your IDE to use the gateway endpoint:\r\n     http://localhost:3000/mcp\r\n\r\n  🛡️  Security features enabled:\r\n"]
[13.154548, "o", "     • Authentication:  STRICT\r\n     • Rate Limiting:   60 req/min\r\n     • CORS:            configured\r\n     • Audit Logging:   enabled\r\n"]
[13.15466, "o", "     • Federation:      3 servers → 1 endpoint\r\n\r\n"]
[15.160563, "o", "\r\n  🚀 Step 4: Start the secured gateway\r\n\r\n"]
[16.167295, "o", "\u001b[1;36m$ mcp-shield start\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[20.17178, "o", "  ✅ Gateway started on port 3000\r\n\r\n  🔍 Step 5: Test security — unauthenticated request\r\n\r\n"]
[21.173433, "o", "\u001b[1;36m$ curl -s -w '\r\nHTTP %{http_code}' -X POST http://localhost:3000/mcp ...\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[22.212292, "o", "{\"error\":\"unauthorized\",\"error_description\":\"JWT token required\"}\r\nHTTP 401\r\n"]
[24.21336, "o", "\r\n  ✅ Request blocked with 401 — authentication required!\r\n"]
[27.214867, "o", "\r\n  📖 Step 6: OAuth discovery metadata is available\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;36m$ curl -s http://localhost:3000/.well-known/oauth-protected-resource/mcp | jq\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[28.234307, "o", "{\r\n    \"resource\": \"http://localhost:3000/mcp\",\r\n    \"authorization_servers\": [\r\n        \"mcp-shield\"\r\n    ],\r\n    \"mcp_protocol_version\": \"2025-06-18\",\r\n    \"resource_type\": \"mcp-server\",\r\n    \"bearer_methods_supported\": [\r\n        \"header\"\r\n    ],\r\n    \"scopes_supported\": [\r\n        \"read:all\",\r\n        \"write:all\",\r\n        \"admin\"\r\n    ]\r\n}\r\n"]
[31.244148, "o", "\r\n  ╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\r\n  ║                                                   ║\r\n  ║   ✅ MCP servers are now secured!                  ║\r\n  ║                                                   ║\r\n  ║   • JWT Authentication (strict mode)              ║\r\n  ║   • Rate Limiting (60 req/min)                    ║\r\n  ║   • CORS configured                               ║\r\n  ║   • 3 servers federated → 1 endpoint              ║\r\n  ║   • OAuth discovery metadata                      ║\r\n  ║                                                   ║\r\n  ║   github.com/bcornish1797/mcp-shield              ║\r\n  ║                                                   ║\r\n  ╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\r\n"]
[31.244182, "o", "\r\n"]
